TITLE: Implementing GitHub OAuth Authentication in React Native with Expo
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to implement GitHub OAuth authentication using the expo-auth-session library in a React Native app. It includes setting up the authentication request, handling the response, and exchanging the code for an access token.
