TITLE: Adding URL Prop Support to iOS WebView Module
DESCRIPTION: Updated Swift module definition that adds a URL prop to the WebView component, allowing the URL to be set from React Native. It includes logic to avoid reloading the same URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/modules/native-view-tutorial.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: swift
CODE:
```
import ExpoModulesCore

public class ExpoWebViewModule: Module {
  public func definition() -> ModuleDefinition {
    Name("ExpoWebView")

    View(ExpoWebView.self) {
      Prop("url") { (view, url: URL) in
        if view.webView.url != url {
          let urlRequest = URLRequest(url: url)
          view.webView.load(urlRequest)
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

