TITLE: Implementing Light Sensor Monitoring in React Native with Expo
DESCRIPTION: A complete example of a React Native component that monitors light sensor data. It demonstrates how to subscribe to illuminance changes, handle component lifecycle with useEffect, and toggle the sensor subscription. The illuminance value is only displayed on Android platforms.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/versions/v53.0.0/sdk/light-sensor.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

