TITLE: Configuring app.config.js with Custom Base Modifiers
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript configuration shows how to use custom base modifiers in an Expo app.config.js file. It demonstrates the proper ordering of plugins, with base modifiers needing to be placed last to ensure they write results to disk after all other modifications.
