DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates basic usage of the `expo-brightness` library within a React Native functional component using Hooks. It requests brightness permissions on component mount using `requestPermissionsAsync` and, if granted, sets the system brightness to maximum (1) using `setSystemBrightnessAsync`. Requires `expo-brightness` dependency.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/versions/v50.0.0/sdk/brightness.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

