TITLE: Generating Video Thumbnail in React Native using expo-video-thumbnails
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the expo-video-thumbnails library to generate a thumbnail image from a video URL. It uses React hooks to manage state and display the generated thumbnail.
