TITLE: Customizing Babel Configuration for Metro (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to customize the Babel configuration for Metro in Expo projects. It demonstrates accessing platform, engine, and environment information from the API caller to conditionally apply plugins and presets.
