TITLE: Using KeepAwake Functions in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the activateKeepAwake and deactivateKeepAwake functions from expo-keep-awake in a React Native component. The activateKeepAwake function keeps the screen on, and deactivateKeepAwake turns this behavior off until it is activated again. Required dependencies: expo-keep-awake.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/versions/unversioned/sdk/keep-awake.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

