CODE:
```
<!--  Auto Backup configuration for Android 12 and higher -->\n<data-extraction-rules>\n  <cloud-backup>\n    <include domain=\"sharedpref\" path=\".\"/>\n    <exclude domain=\"sharedpref\" path=\"SecureStore\"/>\n  </cloud-backup>\n  <device-transfer>\n    <include domain=\"sharedpref\" path=\".\"/>\n    <exclude domain=\"sharedpref\" path=\"SecureStore\"/>\n  </device-transfer>\n</data-extraction-rules>
```

