TITLE: Implementing ReactActivity Listener in Kotlin for Expo Custom Module
DESCRIPTION: This Kotlin code snippet shows the implementation of a ReactActivity listener. It defines a CustomReactActivityLifecycleListener class that overrides the onCreate method to execute static tasks before the JS engine starts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/config-plugins/development-and-debugging.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_9

