TITLE: Rendering Lottie Animation in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the Lottie library in a React Native application. It shows how to render an animation, control it programmatically, and handle user interactions. The example includes a button to restart the animation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/versions/v51.0.0/sdk/lottie.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
