| `global`                   | <YesIcon />   | Set to `globalThis`                                                                                                           |
| `WeakRef`                  | <YesIcon />   | Shim that resets references after each request                                                                                |
| `FinalizationRegistry`     | <NoIcon />    | Garbage collection is not observable within workers                                                                           |
