TITLE: Rewriting URLs in Root Layout Component
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to rewrite URLs within the app using the usePathname hook in the root _layout.tsx file. It demonstrates conditional redirection based on user permissions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/router/advanced/native-intent.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { Slot, Redirect } from 'expo-router';

export default function RootLayout() {
  const pathname = usePathname();

  if (pathname && !isUserAllowed(pathname)) {
    return <Redirect href="/home" />;
  }

  return <Slot />;
}
```

